videos.description: Desmond Bane pokes the ball out of an OSU defender's hands and then rushes to the basket for a strong putback jam.
videos.headline: Bane reaches back and throws down dunk

videos.description: Cameron McGriff takes no prisoners as he drives through traffic for a giant dunk.
videos.headline: McGriff parts the seas with a massive dunk

videos.description: Yor Anei uses his ups to get a crucial block on Alex Robinson as he went for the dunk.
videos.headline: Anei puts down huge block for OSU

videos.description: Yor Anei caps off a 14-0 run from OSU with a beautiful layup to tie the game 68-68.
videos.headline: OSU battles back to tie game with layup from Anei
